To install "Streamlit" use the command :
pip install streamlit
       or
pip3 install streamlit

To install "cv2" use the command :
pip install opencv-python
       or
pip install opencv-contrib-python

To install "NumPy" use the command :
pip install numpy
      
To install "XGBoost" use the command :
pip install xgboost

To install "Ultralytics(YOLOv8)" use the command :
pip install ultralytics

 Verify YOLO is Installed :
 yolo help


